---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-04-25';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now — Arthur Pfalzgraf"
  description="What I'm working on right now."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Now</h1>
    <div class="updated">UPDATED {lastUpdated}</div>
  </header>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Day job">
    <h2>Day job</h2>
    <p>Head of Product at <a href="https://iron.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Iron</a>, now part of MoonPay. Building the stablecoin payments and institutional layer. Heads-down, ship-mode.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Side projects">
    <h2>Side</h2>
    <p>Building my own personal AI stack — a vault that doubles as long-term memory, agents that read and write into it from Telegram, and pipelines that pour content from everywhere I touch into one place.</p>
    <p>Coaching myself toward an Ironman with <a href="https://github.com/Arthurpfz/tri-coach" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">tri-coach</a> — n8n + Claude analysing every workout against the week's plan and texting me feedback. Treating my own training data as the test bed.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Reading and learning">
    <h2>Learning</h2>
    <p>How far you can push small open models with smart routing and tool use. Currently running Grok 4.1 Fast as the default for my agent and only escalating to Sonnet when it actually needs the headroom — about 15× cheaper, no quality cliff so far.</p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <footer class="page-footer">
    <p>Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">nownownow.com</a>. Updated when something changes, not on a schedule.</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-meta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .section {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    border-bottom: var(--border);
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-tag);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-nav);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .section p {
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  hr {
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .page-footer {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .page-footer p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    opacity: 0.45;
  }
</style>
